{"tid":56254,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"26 斜路八字","createTime":"2016-12-27T06:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T23:31:02.000Z","uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e32740c784c650203321a9a7afc5465c869f849","tid":56254,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"今日上完導師堂岀街都無咩問題<br />\n本身揸開車<br />\n但係打八字方面想請教咁多位巴打<br />\n我上到頂落番黎個位掌握得唔係幾好<br />\n有無咩心得可以教下細佬？？<br />\n我諗係自己轉得太急夾手定唔到油<br />\n上番去都無乜問題<br />\n唔知咁多位有無咩打8字心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n棍<br />\n本身諗住考到牌出gsxs750 點知自己連8字都打得唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ee46c3df9fd58edabda1079d2c824367d01795","tid":56254,"uid":31089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"老生常談，唔好咁早cut油"},{"pid":"872aafcd61e52e5c71254c5e55eac11608613fd4","tid":56254,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"你係冇腦？<br />\n冇老先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1982ac6ba44636804209da8b6e7bb8aced5c139","tid":56254,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:39:44.000Z","msg":"個八字唔好打咁尖. 用盡條路個闊度, 等自己有多D時間攞直架車. 盡量近邊位先扭胎. 車速我個人覺得越快越好."},{"pid":"733e5d8fc326cdeac244538ed21fa2adf9cd105e","tid":56254,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係冇腦？<br />\n冇老先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係"},{"pid":"1ff8363593a944a2f06fb7fa7c7e7788d3646a6c","tid":56254,"uid":10790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個八字唔好打咁尖. 用盡條路個闊度, 等自